msgid "Elementor Pro Theme Builder: Single Product Template Detected"
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-wc-gallery-admin.php
msgid "<strong>Elementor Pro Theme Builder</strong> is controlling the single product layout. This overrides WooCommerce's template system, so our gallery hook is bypassed and the gallery will not appear."
