msgid "Oxygen Builder: Product Template Detected"
msgstr ""

#: includes/admin/class-wc-gallery-admin.php
msgid "<strong>Oxygen Builder</strong> has a template assigned to single product pages. Oxygen renders pages independently of WordPress's template loop, so WooCommerce's gallery hook does not fire."
